abstract_ssm: Mike Topp is a poet, editor, and member of The Unbearables, a loosely organized group of Downtown writers and artists, known for protests against notions of "good" or "bad" literature and art. This collection consists of Topp's poem drafts and idea notes, plus published works he contributed to and edited.
